---
title: Asian Beef Strips & Peanut Sauce Tacos with Creamy Sesame Slaw & Plant-Based Mayonnaise
description: What happens when you combine the flavours of Mexico and Asia into one dish? A whole new take on tacos you
didn’t know you needed! Golden beef strips and creamy sesame slaw are nestled into a warm tortilla, then drizzled with a delightfully nutty peanut sauce. Yum!

*We’ve replaced the crispy shallots in this recipe with spring onion due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
